com.jgaap.generics
Class EventHistogram

java.lang.Object
  com.jgaap.generics.EventHistogram

public class EventHistogram
extends java.lang.Object

Class supporting basic histogram operations on Events. Uses a Hashtable to keep track of events and their counts, and provides standard access methods.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Juola
